## Sections Pattern
- Each section: `<section id="slug" ref={...} className="mb-20 scroll-mt-20">`
- Section H2: `text-xl lg:text-3xl font-bold font-['Inter'] leading-7 lg:leading-10`
- Body copy: `text-base font-normal lg:font-medium font-['Inter'] leading-6`
- Large body: `text-base lg:text-lg font-normal lg:font-medium font-['Inter'] leading-6 lg:leading-7`
- Dividers between sections: `<hr className="border-t border-gray-200 my-16" />`

## Load More Pattern (mobile pagination)
